      About this item

      • UNMATCHED POWER – From our Titanium steel 4 blade rotation system, to our full copper 800 watt clump destroying motor, no other stick blender matches this model's ability to crush, pulverize, and smoothly blend, so any recipe or smoothie can be made with the easiest cleanup.
      • PRECISE CONTROL - 12-speeds give you maximum choice and precision to prepare salsas, shakes, smoothies, baby food, and more! 800 Watts of power drives consistently smooth results and high performance. Use the TURBO boost for maximum speed and a more homogeneous mixture.
      • MULTI-FUNCTIONAL MASTERY - Beyond blending, our comprehensive set includes a Snap-on Whisk attachment, Beaker (20 fl. oz) and Twist and Lock Chopper (16oz) with removable blade, redefining the 3-in-1 kitchen appliance concept. The chopper acts as your mini food processor with the perfect lid to eliminate mess and tearing eyes when chopping white or red onions!
      • CONVENIENCE AT ITS BEST - The hand mixer is designed with a comfy grip handle for a non-slip, comfortable hold, and a sleek body that fits into mixing bowls and pots of all sizes. Simplify your cleaning process with our easy-to-detach, dishwasher-safe parts, and enjoy the stability of a non-slip base during use.
      • LIVE CUSTOMER CARE – Talk to us via our toll-free number or live chat, not via email like our competitors. Mueller believes in making life easier, better and more enjoyable in all that we do. Our total satisfaction promise covers all our products. If you need any help, please feel free to contact us.

        Smart Stick

        Merchant Video
        Previous page

        1. 4 Titanium Rotary Blades with 800W Strength, for consistently smooth results every time!

        3. This immersion blender has everything, including a Whisk attachment, 2.5 Cup Beaker/ Measuring Cup, and 2-Cup Twist & Lock Chopper!

        4. Puree directly into your cookware! The blender fits most pots, bowls, and beakers, and the unique bell shape reduces suction & splashing.

        5. Each part easily detaches for quick clean-up and is top-rack dishwasher safe. Save on storage space with just this one great 4-in-1 device.

        Next page

        • Does the hand blender come with any practical kitchen accessories?

          The 5-in-1 blender and food processor combo includes an immersion blender handheld, detachable blending stick, detachable electric whisk, detachable milk frother, 2-cup mini food processor, and 2.5 cup beaker for blending of sauces and smoothies.

        • Is it suitable as a smoothie blender?

          Most definitely! You can add your ingredients into the smoothie beaker provided, then use the blending attachment to blend until smooth. Use turbo mode for tougher ingredients.

        • How powerful is its motor?

          The Multistick Hand blender features a 800W with 12 speed options and turbo mode. Blend delicate sauces or chunky soups in no time.

        • Is it suitable for blending hot liquids safely without splattering?

          The blender fits most pots, bowls, and beakers, and the unique bell shape reduces suction & splashing so you can safely blend soups and hot liquids directly in your cookware.

        • Is it easy to clean and dishwasher safe?

          Yes! For the easiest clean, place the blending stick in hot soapy water and blend! All parts are fully detachable, and top-rack dishwasher safe.

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        • Carolina Shopper
          4.0 out of 5 stars Good value for the price
          Reviewed in the United States on March 29, 2025
          Color: GreyVerified Purchase
          Interesting story behind this purchase... We weren't really looking for a handheld/immersion blender (we already have one), but we were shopping for a corded frother to replace the battery powered ones we keep buying and burning through. We ran across this Mueller multi-function handheld, which includes a frother, and was on a good sale, so we decided to give it a try. This Mueller model has more functionality than our previous handheld, which is single function (and still works great BTW), and includes a frother wand attachment. The frother attachment works okay, but it has a "wobble" to it, perhaps because it's a longer device, so it takes longer to get the same foam level. The immersion blender attachment works great, but remember not to use it on coated cookware (just like any metal utensils). The single whisk attachment is handy for small whipping jobs. The chopper container is nice to have for small chopping jobs, but you do need to break things down a bit beforehand. Regardless of the attachment you're using, the instructions say to not operate the motor for more than a minute at a time, so this is a lightweight device for small jobs. But it is versatile, and I appreciate the function. It will definitely save getting out a larger appliance for small jobs.
